title: Lake Mead National Recreation Area: Grad 2016
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Education     Grad 2016               Grad 2016              In 2009, to commemorate the 100th anniversary of the National Park Service, Lake Mead National Recreation Area partnered with the graduating class of 2016 of several area schools. The goal of the partnership is to connect these students with a variety of experiences each year until their graduation in 2016.             Grad 2016   Loading the player...
